;;-----------------------------------------------------------------
;;  extended display (messge window and model window) document file
;;-----------------------------------------------------------------



* (change-display {option}) 

  where option is either l u a n
  {option} : l  - lower window (model window) display
             u  - upper window (message window) display
             a  - all window display
             n  - no display

*  (change-display) for default display mode (all windows displayed)
